title: The Chase’s Jenny Ryan leaves viewers ‘speechless’ on X Factor: Celebrity
text:
Jenny Ryan wowed the judges (Picture: ITV/Rex)

The Chase’s Jenny Ryan shocked viewers with her incredible singing skills on X Factor: Celebrity.

The 37-year-old quizmaster, otherwise known as The Vixen on The Chase, delivered a stunning cover of Queen’s Somebody To Love on the ITV show.

After earning a standing ovation from the judges, Louis Walsh said: ‘Wow Jenny, where did all that come from? You’ve got a great voice.’

Nicole Scherzinger added: ‘Jenny, you were like, “I don’t really care y’all… Welcome to my back garden.”

‘To know that you’re like a human encyclopaedia or whatever – when you opened your face hole and that came out, I was like, “Yeah!”’

Viewers were similarly in agreement – picking Jenny as an early favourite.

Do we have our winner already?
